paper_abstract: The five functionals fixed-point theorem is applied to investigate the existence of at least three positive solutions of boundary value problems for the one-dimensional p-Laplacian dynamic equations on time scales. As an application, two examples are given to illustrate the main results in this paper. (c) 2006 Elsevier Ltd. All rights reserved.
paper_title: Multiple positive solutions for the one-dimensional p-Laplacian dynamic equations on time scales
